  ],
  "content": "Sendable Post — WhatsApp Group InviteCopy the text below and paste it into Sendable, email, or social posts.Join our WhatsApp Group — Police Station Rep UK (England & Wales) Real-time opportunities, networking and updates for accredited professionals. Eligibility (IMPORTANT): • Police station representatives or criminal solicitors only (freelance or employed) • Fully accredited only — not training or awaiting accreditation • Proof required (e.g. LCCSA/CLSA membership, Duty Solicitor status, or firm confirmation) • Verification checks will be made with the Law Society and the Legal Aid Agency • Closed group — not open to the public How to join: 1) Read the full details: https://policestationrepuk.co.uk/WhatsApp 2) Message us on WhatsApp: 07535 494446 (messages only) By applying, you confirm you meet the above requirements. Copy",
